{"tid":1022722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲正妹遭性侵「暴肥300公斤」　贅肉垂地寸步難行！","createTime":"2019-02-15T08:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T08:28:52.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2869be18672dff10f0129f323ac2e8e83342306","tid":1022722,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3897/d3897828.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3897%2Fd3897828.jpg&h=5aed149e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲艾莉卡為了「不再受到男人注意」，開始暴飲暴食，體重激增至300公斤。（圖／翻攝自youtube）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國加州的艾莉卡（Erica Wall）在16歲時遭受性侵，接著又經歷母親過世的悲劇，為了建立「保護色」，她開始「暴飲暴食」，體重飆升至300公斤，肚子的肉更直接垂到膝蓋，全身上下淋巴水腫，直到生活及健康方面出現許多困難時，才下定決心減重，不僅減去了183公斤，還遇到了真命天子。<br />\n艾莉卡在16歲時遭到初戀男友欺騙，被逼與男友的堂哥及朋友上床，從此在心裡留下嚴重陰影，她開始暴飲暴食，把自己建立在一層厚厚的「防護肉層」裡，她認為，這樣就不會有男生再靠近了。不過這讓艾莉卡有了食物成癮的問題，體重直線飆升到300公斤，全身上下淋巴水腫，尤其是腳部非常嚴重，導致她的行走困難，讓她的身體更加虛弱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3897/d3897829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3897%2Fd3897829.jpg&h=96471400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲艾莉卡肚子的肉垂到膝蓋，讓她不良於行。（圖／翻攝自youtube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3898/d3898226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3898%2Fd3898226.jpg&h=0d3f5176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲艾莉卡小腿上的贅肉至少十層。（圖／翻攝自TLC YouTube）<br />\n在健康持續惡化的情況下，艾莉卡意識到自己再不減肥隨時都可能面臨死亡，因此她決定開啟一場「剷肉工程」，並到德州休士頓求助名醫師納查拉登。這趟求醫之行可說是備加艱辛，艾麗卡表示，因為自己的體型太過龐大，航空公司因此要求她買下整排3個座位，讓她感慨自己「淪落成別人的餘興節目」，甚至到了醫院後，還因身體不適被緊急送醫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3897/d3897729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3897%2Fd3897729.jpg&h=674c4f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲艾莉卡成功減了183公斤，還遇到了自己的真愛。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／Erica Lynn Wall）<br />\n艾莉卡在納查拉登醫師的幫助下手術去掉多餘脂肪，並改善過去「食物上癮」的症狀，避免暴飲暴食。艾莉卡在活動及飲食控制上做出努力後，成功減去了183公斤，不僅遇到自己的真愛，也有自信穿上泳衣到海邊，重新找回人生的意義。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2_GgGqwPJ00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2_GgGqwPJ00&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=b93cf10d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2_GgGqwPJ00</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190215/1378724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190215%2F1378724.htm&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=4a346caa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190215/1378724.htm</a>"},{"pid":"36ae6436ae3e5fa9c1f83673df52c40632f87016","tid":1022722,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/231534_3807eb3d28c21da70cd9a93638ff7fe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F231534_3807eb3d28c21da70cd9a93638ff7fe4.jpg&h=7b37f16c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52a5a997a8ec1b5ad6f8091cc8df443deead2aa6","tid":1022722,"uid":10056,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"一個人可以食到咁肥真係好令人驚嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d254c51e4f1e7562cacd8557b052f3ee2a5c6140","tid":1022722,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:25:57.000Z","msg":"呢張唔知點解有啲正 我係咪傻撚左<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3897/d3897829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3897%2Fd3897829.jpg&h=5bd4ef72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38057e4027dd111e8ca27d220d690c7758aab451","tid":1022722,"uid":161892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:28:52.000Z","msg":"佢既計劃好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}